Convert a space separated set of data into a tabular form for easier readability

Usage example

❯ cat scores.txt  
Name Subject Score
Bryan Arts 68
Isaiah Arts 80
Gabriel Health-Medicine 100
Tysza Business 92
Zackery Engineering 54

❯ column -t scores.txt                
Name     Subject          Score
Bryan    Arts             68
Isaiah   Arts             80
Gabriel  Health-Medicine  100
Tysza    Business         92
Zackery  Engineering      54

❯ column -t scores.txt > myscores.txt

❯ cat myscores.txt 
Name     Subject          Score
Bryan    Arts             68
Isaiah   Arts             80
Gabriel  Health-Medicine  100
Tysza    Business         92
Zackery  Engineering      54
